doc.after: Microsoft Campus is the informal name for Microsoft s corporate headquarters located at One Microsoft Way in Redmond Washington Microsoft initially moved onto the grounds of the campus on February 26 1986 weeks before the company went public on March 13 The headquarters has since experienced multiple expansions since its establishment
